<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8"
	pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet"
	href="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/css/member_style/slidebar.css">

<link rel="stylesheet"
	href="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/css/member_style/adoption.css">
</head>

	<div class="content-title">	
	<h1><b>입양절차</b></h1>
</div>
<div class="info-box">
	<img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image//adoption/caution_1.png"
	alt="주의">
	새로운 가족에게 사랑을 나누세요! HomeSweetHome 입양절차에 대해 알려 드립니다.
</div>
<div class="content-body">
			
 <div class="step-container">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="step">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image//adoption/online_1.png" alt="Step 1 Icon" class="step-icon">
            <div class="step-content">
                <h3>1. 입양 전 교육(온라인)</h3>
                <p>입양을 희망하시는 분은 "입양자 교육"을 이수해 주세요.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="step-button">입양자교육바로가기 ➔</a>
        </div>

        <!-- 화살표 -->
        <div class="arrow">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image//adoption/progress_1.png" alt="Step 2 Icon" class="step-icon">
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="step">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image//adoption/check_1.png" alt="Step 2 Icon" class="step-icon">
            <div class="step-content">
                <h3>2. 적합성검진표</h3>
                <p>온라인 교육 이수 후 검진표를 작성해주세요.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="step-button">적합성검진표 바로가기 ➔</a>
        </div>

        <!-- 화살표 -->
        <div class="arrow">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image//adoption/progress_1.png" alt="Step 2 Icon" class="step-icon">
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="step">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image/adoption/calendar_1.png" alt="Step 3 Icon" class="step-icon">
            <div class="step-content">
                <h3>3. 센터방문예약(방문상담)</h3>
                <p>센터 방문 예정일과 시간을 선택하여 예약해주세요.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="step-button">예약 바로가기 ➔</a>
        </div>

        <!-- 화살표 -->
        <div class="arrow">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image//adoption/progress_1.png" alt="Step 2 Icon" class="step-icon">
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="step">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image//adoption/application_1.png" alt="Step 4 Icon" class="step-icon">
            <div class="step-content">
                <h3>4. 입양신청</h3>
                <p>앞선 절차를 진행하신 사용자만 신청이 가능합니다.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="step-button">입양신청 ➔</a>
        </div>

        <!-- 화살표 -->
        <div class="arrow">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image//adoption/progress_1.png" alt="Step 2 Icon" class="step-icon">
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="step">
            <img src="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/resources/image/adoption/review_1.png" alt="Step 5 Icon" class="step-icon">
            <div class="step-content">
                <h3>5. 입양후기 작성</h3>
                <p>입양후기 게시판에 입양된 동물의 행복한 일상을 공유해주세요.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="step-button">후기 작성 ➔</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>